::Magmatron::

    "I understand." Magmatron said. "But you must wear that on your arm, 
unless you like being blasted into subatomic particles. My autoguns are 
programmed to reconize only Destron signals."
    "Now Bazooka will you show our new troops to their quarters?" Magmatron 
asked Bazooka. "I'm sure you find them quite pleasant." Magmatron said to 
Shredder and Mantella.
